Package ca.ualberta.cs.c301_teamproject

Class Summary
CreateItem This class will create a item for a task.
CreateTask This class is responsible for grabbing all of the information needed for creating a task then passes it off to the repository for creation.
FileBrowser This class is a modified version of the code given by Androider+ in the following URL: http://android-er.blogspot.ca/2010/01 /implement-simple-file-explorer-in.html
InputAudio Records, plays and saves audio to .3ga format.
InputFile Import or capture files/items to be added to a task.
InputText This class creates an input text menu that will take a user's input and generate a text file at a set location and add it to the file list.
ItemList Displays a listview of files for a given item in a task.
ItemListAdapter Custom ListAdapter for Task Force's multiline, with icon, ListView.
ItemListElement Class for elements of multi-element listview in ItemList.
MainPage This class just has the buttons for the main page.
MyLocalTaskInformation This class is used to store taskIDs locally for both myTask and myLikes.
PromptDialog Custom dialog screens for Task Force.
TaskProperties This class is just used to gather the task properties.
ViewSingleTask This class shows items for a task in a list, click item to view.
ViewTasks This class is used for viewing a list of all the tasks.
WelcomePage This class is the welcome page, any click on the screen will move yor forward
